QuestData.Title: Dances with Grimtotem
QuestData.Description: Return now to your leader and tell him all that you have done for the Grimtotem. Tell him that the Alliance may pass freely across our borders.
QuestData.LogDescription: Report to Force Commander Valen at Northwatch Expedition Base Camp in Stonetalon Mountains.
QuestData.RewardText: Outstanding work, $n! Now our forces only need to worry about the Horde as they enter Stonetalon.
